裔人人都係阿里、阿星、穆罕默德？<br />\n<br />\n本以為同中文名阿華、國強一樣，阿里、穆罕默德係最受歡迎的名字，原來是一個誤會。早期很多少數族裔不懂中文，搵社工或老師改名，由於認識不深，他們將所有姓 Ali 的都改為阿里、所有姓 Mohanmad 的都變穆罕默德，所有印度男鍚克教徒因為姓 Singh ，所以都叫阿星，就似人人都係阿陳同阿張， 沒有自己的名字。<br />\n<br />\n前融樂會總幹事王惠芬講過幾個一聽難忘的名字：<br />\n<br />\n三姐妹姓 Malik ，社工幫她們改了<span style=\"color: red;\">孖力大、孖力二、孖力三</span>。<br />\n兩個同班小男生都叫 Tariq ，老師幫他們改了<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>苦力、大力</strong></span>。<br />\n姐姐 Mariam ，老師改馬利安，妹妹 Fatima ，改了李小冰；經常被問為何姊妹不同姓，她們的姓 Khan 卻沒有了。<br />\n尼泊爾男孩 Gurung Jesh ，有區議員幫他改為古龍爵士，或者想引人誤會有位爵士撐場吧，男孩後來知道非常尷尬，但已被寫入身份證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源: <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C-%E9%98%BF%E6%98%9F-%E7%A9%86%E7%BD%95%E9%BB%98%E5%BE%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%25A3%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%2598%25BF%25E9%2587%258C-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%2598%259F-%25E7%25A9%2586%25E7%25BD%2595%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%25BE%25B7%2F&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=b484ea9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%25A3%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%2598%25BF%25E9%2587%258C-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%2598%259F-%25E7%25A9%2586%25E7%25BD%2595%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%25BE%25B7%2F&h=7231edfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C-%E9%98%BF%E6%98%9F-%E7%A9%86%E7%BD%95%E9%BB%98%E5%BE%B7/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"Fatima Khan 姦肥媽<br />\nMariam Khan 姦媽你淫"},{"pid":"b8a6e6c0af6ac4d87b903b6aaebfd46f12f8911c","tid":1017413,"uid":28624,"like"